"RosalieArrivalCTMarried2": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#Hi sweetheart, #$b# I'm sorry I've been spacing out a lot since the new patient came to town.$s #$b# I've just been bothered by something lately...$7 #$b# $y 'Is it about her case?_That's part of it, I won't lie! You know me so well!$h_What's wrong with her?_Your choice of phrasing leaves much to be desired,@.$5_Harvey, you can tell me anything!_I know, that's what I love about us.$4 #$b# But I can't tell you anything about her medical history._Anything I can help with?_No, but thank you my love.$1' #$b# I just feel like I've met Rosalie before, but I'm unsure where.$2",


