//ROSALIES EVENT CT//
"Harvey.RosalieGeorgeWCCT": "$p RosalieGeorgeWC3#I didn't tell Rosalie what you said. But I hope Gus changed your mind.$a|I tried to call to see how Rosalie was doing after last night...$s #$b#She says she's fine, but I'm not sure I believe her...$s",
"Harvey.RosaliesFlareUpCT": "I think that the fact that Rosalie is going through a divroce isn't a bad thing at all. #$b# It was very brave of her to leave a relationship that wasn't serving her. Especilaly a toxic one at that.$s #$e# His behaviour speaks more for him than it does for her. I'm glad she sought help in her family, and myself.$s #$e# Sometimes two people aren't meant to be together.$s #$b# Now that Rose and I have gotten close enough for her to open up, I'm amazed at how much patience and resilience she had because she loved him so much, and still manage to stay kind. #$e# I hope... I hope she finds someone who wouldn't take that for granted...$2 #$e# I wouldn't… $b",



