//VANILLA DO NOT CHANGE!!!//

"Harvey.Introduction": "It's a pleasure to meet you. I'm Harvey, the local doctor.#$e#I perform regular check-ups and medical procedures for all the residents of Pelican Town. It's rewarding work.#$e#I hope you'll find your own work equally rewarding, in time.$h",
"Harvey.AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive": "Oh! Thank you very much! I didn't expect anyone to know it was my birthday today.$h",
"Harvey.AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative": "Oh! It's a... well, it's something. I didn't expect anyone to know it was my birthday today.",
"Harvey.AcceptGift(O)StardropTea": "You're giving me this? I'm honored. Thank you!",
"Harvey.FlowerDance_Accept": "Oh! You... want to dance with me?$4#$b#...Yes. I'd love to!$h",
"Harvey.GreenRain": "I brought some medical supplies, just in case. Be careful out there!",
"Harvey.GreenRain_2": "The first time this happened, we were all worried that the rain might be dangerous.#$b#But what if it's actually healthy for the body? Who knows... The plants seem to respond well to it, at least.",
"Harvey.AcceptGift(O)432": "It's for me? Thank you! This will be fantastic drizzled on some pasta.$h",
"Harvey.AcceptGift(O)348": "For me? What a gift! This looks fantastic!$h#$b#You know, on a physiological level, I wouldn't advise the consumption of alcohol...#$b#But there's no denying the benefit of kicking back and enjoying a glass of fine Stardew Valley wine!$h",
"Harvey.eventSeen_56_memory_fourweeks": "I've been working on an 'animal checklist' for a few years now. I want to observe every species living in the valley!",
"Harvey.eventSeen_56_memory_twoweeks": "I tried making my own pickles one time...$s#$e#Um, let me put it this way... The frogs we dissected in high school smelled like roses in comparison...",
"Harvey.eventSeen_56": "As a small town doctor, you can't help but form a personal connection with your patients. That can be both good and bad...",
"Harvey.eventSeen_58_memory_oneweek": "Well now that you know my secret, I might as well give you an update... I was significantly less winded after aerobics class this week!",
"Harvey.eventSeen_58_memory_twoweeks": "I got such a good workout during aerobics class, I think I can treat myself to some pasta primavera tonight...$h",
"Harvey.eventSeen_58_memory_fourweeks": "I don't know why I was ashamed about being in dance aerobics class. My legs have become so strong, I should feel as bold as a lion!",
"Harvey.eventSeen_571102_memory": "I've never told anyone about my airplane hobby before... I guess I just feel comfortable talking to you.",
"Harvey.eventSeen_571102_memory_oneweek": "As a doctor, you can only do so much to help your patients...#$e#I've made the mistake of getting too emotionally involved in the past... I won't let that happen again...$s",
"Harvey.dating_Harvey": "I've never felt like this before...$l",
"Harvey.dating_Harvey_memory_oneday": "I've been thinking about you so much, I can hardly do my work.$l",
"Harvey.dating_Maru_memory_oneday": "Maru's been unusually cheerful lately... I hear you may have something to do with that.",
"Harvey.married_Maru": "Congratulations on your marriage, @. Maru's already informed me that she'll continue to work at the clinic, which is a relief!",
"Harvey.married_Harvey": "This is the happiest moment of my life...$l",
"Harvey.Resort_Entering": "Sunscreen? Check...#$b#Sun hat? Check...",
"Harvey.Resort_Leaving": "If you get burnt, a little aloe vera cream might help soothe the skin.",
"Harvey.Resort_Shore": "I combed the whole beach for glass. We wouldn't want anyone to get a cut on their foot!",
"Harvey.Resort_Chair": "It's nice to have an opportunity to relax now and then.#$b#The trouble is actually letting go of your worries...$s",
"Harvey.Resort_Bar": "It's important to stay hydrated in this heat. I'm going to ask Gus if he has any coconut water!$h",
"Harvey.Resort": "I'll let you in on a little secret... I can only swim with floaties.$s",
"Harvey.FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse": "I've been looking forward to it all afternoon! You look radiant in the fresh spring air, my love.$l",
"Harvey.FlowerDance_Decline": "Oh! I'm sorry... I, er... have plans to ask someone else.$s",
"Harvey.divorced": "I... I can't look at you. Please spare me any more pain.$s",
"Harvey.breakUp": "...Y...You...?$s#$b#*gulp*... I... I think I'm going to be sick...$s",
"Harvey.dumped_Guys": "I'm busy with my work. I can't speak to you.$s",
"Harvey.secondChance_Guys": "I want you back in my life, @. I'm willing to forget what happened.$s",
"Harvey.Mon": "We sell a few over-the-counter medicines at the clinic... feel free to stop by if you're feeling exhausted.#$b#I know that being a farmer is pretty tiring work... don't overdo it!",
"Harvey.Mon2": "I feel responsible for the health of this whole community... it's kind of stressful.#$e#It's a pretty small community, and I'm fortunate to be able to build a good relationship with my patients.",
"Harvey.Mon6": "I'd like to stay in Stardew Valley for a while. I'm finally starting to feel involved in the community.#$e#It feels good to know that you're useful.",
"Harvey.Mon10": "Oh! Hi, @.$l#$e#Do you... have any medical questions?$l",
"Harvey.Tue": "Feel free to stop by my office if you're ever feeling ill.#$e#You're young, though. You'll probably stay healthy without trying.$h",
"Harvey.Tue8": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#Don't overwork yourself, @. Doctor's orders!#$e#If our farmers get sick, where will we get our food? We need you!$h|Don't overwork yourself, @. Doctor's orders!#$e#Your health is important to me.$l",
"Harvey.Wed4": "I'd like to get to know you better, @. Let's put aside our doctor-patient relationship.",
"Harvey.Wed6": "It's nice to have a friend in town.$h",
"Harvey.Wed8": "You have a really healthy glow. That's good.$h",
"Harvey.Wed": "Remember to cover your mouth when you sneeze.#$e#Then make sure to wash your hands.",
"Harvey.Thu8": "$query PLAYER_NPC_RELATIONSHIP current any married roommate#As a doctor, I'm well aware of the benefits of home-cooked food. But I'm so busy, I have a hard time bringing myself to cook.$s|It's a lot of work, being a doctor. I don't eat as well as I should.$s#$e#If I didn't live alone I think it would be easier.$l",
"Harvey.Thu": "Nutrition is important, so make sure and eat well. Try to increase your vegetable intake!#$e#Home-cooked meals are best. Do you cook?",
"Harvey.Fri": "It's a beautiful day, isn't it?#$e#I wish I had less work to do.$s",
"Harvey.Fri4": "If you want to hang out in my apartment, that's okay with me. I live above the clinic.",
"Harvey.Fri10": "Stop by my place if you ever need a confidential check-up.$l",
"Harvey.Sat": "Can I do anything for you?#$e#Take care.",
"Harvey.Sat4": "I came here because I liked the small-town atmosphere, and the potential for a holistic approach to patient care.#$e#I've grown to really love it.$h",
"Harvey.Sat10": "*Sigh*... I'm starting to feel kind of old...#$e#The older you get the more memories you're burdened with. It can be overwhelming.$s#$e#I think I'll stay younger with you around.$l",
"Harvey.Sun": "Hmm... I'm struggling to make ends meet. I don't have enough patients.#$e#I guess I should try to get patients from the neighboring towns...",
"Harvey.Sun6": "Imagine having a patient's life completely in your hands, and failing to keep them alive... that's something that will haunt you forever.$s",
"Harvey.summer_Mon": "It's okay to get a moderate amount of sunlight. Just don't get burnt.#$e#Okay. Take care! Stay healthy.",
"Harvey.summer_Thu": "Exercise is important, but don't get too exhausted, or you might end up at my clinic!#$e#Make sure and listen to your body.",
"Harvey.summer_Fri": "People don't get sick much during the summer. That's nice, but it also means less business for me.",
"Harvey.fall_Fri": "Have you been going into the mines, @?#$e#It's a dangerous place. I recommend against it.",
"Harvey.fall_Sat": "When you eat certain foods you'll perform better.#$e#Eating a 'Farmer's Lunch' will give you the nutrition you need to water and harvest crops better!",
"Harvey.winter_Wed": "It's flu season, so you'd better be extra careful.#$e#Make sure to wash your hands often.",
"Harvey.winter_Sun": "I hate to say this, but I do make a lot more money during flu season.#$e#I guess if people stopped getting sick, I'd be out of business.#$e#Don't get the wrong idea! I want people to be healthy... really!",

}